---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy Policy for NameGen Name Generator website."
>
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto space-y-6">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-[#111111] dark:text-white">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-[#666666] dark:text-[#888888]">Last Updated: July 2, 2026</p>
    
    <div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-[#666666] dark:text-[#888888] leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        At NameGen, we are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy describes how we handle information on our website.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#111111] dark:text-white mt-6">1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>Local Storage:</strong> We use your browser's local storage (localStorage) to save your favorited names. This data remains on your local device and is never sent to our servers. We do not run databases or tracking profiles on individuals.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Analytics:</strong> We may use basic, anonymized web analytics to monitor overall traffic levels and popular features. This does not identify you individually.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#111111] dark:text-white mt-6">2. Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>
        We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your information to third parties. There are no advertising scripts or external tracking platforms on our site.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#111111] dark:text-white mt-6">3. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We reserve the right to update this policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
